# UI Components

The application uses [Shadcn UI](mdc:https:/ui.shadcn.com) for its component library, with customizations for the form builder.

## Core UI Components

- [components/ui/form.tsx](mdc:components/ui/form.tsx): Form component with React Hook Form integration
- [components/ui/button.tsx](mdc:components/ui/button.tsx): Button component with variants
- [components/ui/card.tsx](mdc:components/ui/card.tsx): Card components for layout
- [components/ui/dialog.tsx](mdc:components/ui/dialog.tsx): Modal dialog components

## Data Display Components

- [components/data-table.tsx](mdc:components/data-table.tsx): Advanced data table with sorting, filtering, and pagination
- [components/ui/table.tsx](mdc:components/ui/table.tsx): Basic table components
- [components/chart-area-interactive.tsx](mdc:components/chart-area-interactive.tsx): Interactive area charts

## Navigation Components

- [components/app-sidebar.tsx](mdc:components/app-sidebar.tsx): Application sidebar
- [components/nav-main.tsx](mdc:components/nav-main.tsx): Main navigation
- [components/site-header.tsx](mdc:components/site-header.tsx): Site header
- [components/nav-user.tsx](mdc:components/nav-user.tsx): User navigation

